items.Title: BMW M3 GTR GT,E46
items.info:
BMW’s early-2000s GT race weapon (made iconic by NFS: Most Wanted). A 4.0L V8 powers the racer, built for endurance-series domination.

Power: ~450 hp • Weight: ~1,100 kg • Top speed: ~260 km/h
